messages.body_plain:
with tiger and gcc-4.x use gfortran-4.x (either from cvs or
from gaurav's site). then setenv gcc /usr/local/bin/gfortran.

also gcc 4061 is a bit old -- the tiger update in 10.4.2 was
50xx, i think, cvs is up to apple build 5217 and is now
gcc-4.0.1.

-- jan

